vulnerability.name: USN-7014-1
vulnerability.description: It was discovered that the nginx ngx_http_mp4 module incorrectly handled certain malformed mp4 files. In environments where the mp4 directive is in use, a remote attacker could possibly use this issue to cause nginx to crash, resulting in a denial of service.

statements.status_notes: nginx could be made to crash if it received specially crafted network traffic.
